{"article_id":"4Gci6WBO7UEQC2jp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Saudi Arabia rejects political and economic `` threats '' over missing journalist Jamal Khashoggi ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"a source","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"quoted by state news agency SPA","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"says .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"The country would respond to any punitive action `` with a bigger one '' ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"the unnamed senior source said .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Mr Khashoggi , a critic of the Saudi government , vanished on 2 October","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"after visiting its consulate in Istanbul .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"US President Donald Trump said","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"he would `` punish '' Saudi Arabia","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"if it were found responsible for killing him .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"On Sunday a joint statement by the foreign ministers of the UK , France and Germany called for a credible investigation","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"to ensure","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"those responsible for Mr Khashoggi 's disappearance were held to account .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"`` We encourage joint Saudi-Turkish efforts in that regard ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"and expect the Saudi Government to provide a complete and detailed response , ''","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"said Jeremy Hunt , Jean-Yves Le Drian and Heiko Maas .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Later Mr Hunt said","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that whatever happened now was `` absolutely up to Saudi Arabia '' .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"`` If ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"as they say ,","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"this terrible murder did n't happen ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"then where is Jamal Khashoggi ?","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"That 's what the world wants to know . ''","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Britain and the US are considering boycotting a major international conference in Saudi Arabia this month .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"The authorities in Istanbul believe","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Mr Khashoggi was murdered in the consulate by Saudi agents","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"- claims","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Riyadh has dismissed as `` lies '' .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"The source","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"quoted by SPA","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"said :","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"`` The kingdom affirms","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"its total rejection of any threats or attempts","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"to undermine it","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"whether through threats","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"to impose economic sanctions or the use of political pressure .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"`` The kingdom also affirms","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"that it will respond to any action with a bigger one .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"The Saudi economy has vital and influential roles for the global economy . ''","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"But on Sunday evening King Salman appeared more conciliatory ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"thanking Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"for setting up a joint team","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"to investigate the disappearance .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"No-one could undermine the strong relationship","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Saudi Arabia had with Turkey ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"The Saudis have come under considerable international pressure over the disappearance .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Diplomatic sources told the BBC 's James Landale","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"that both US Treasury Secretary Steve Mnuchin and UK International Trade Secretary Liam Fox might not attend next month 's investment conference in Riyadh ,","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"which has been dubbed `` Davos in the Desert '' .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"However , later White House aide Larry Kudlow told ABC News","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"as things stood","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"Mr Mnuchin was intending to go to Riyadh","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"and would take a final decision `` as new information surfaces '' .","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"The event is being hosted by the kingdom 's Crown Prince Mohamed bin Salman","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"to promote his reform agenda .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Several sponsors and media groups have decided to pull out .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"A joint statement of condemnation ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"if it is confirmed that Mr Khashoggi was killed by Saudi agents ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"is also being discussed by US and European diplomats .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"The president has said","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"the US will inflict `` severe punishment ''","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"if Saudi Arabia is found to be responsible for the death of Mr Khashoggi .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"he would be `` very upset and angry","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"if that were the case '' ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"but ruled out halting big military contracts .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"we 'd be punishing ourselves","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"if we did that , ''","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"`` If they do n't buy it from us ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"they 're going to buy it from Russia or ... China . ''","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"Turkish Foreign Minister Mevut Cavusoglu said","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Saudi Arabia had not so far co-operated with the investigation","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"- despite a statement from Saudi Interior Minister Prince Abdulaziz bin Saud bin Naif bin Abdulaziz","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"his nation wanted to uncover `` the whole truth '' .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Mr Cavusoglu has urged the kingdom to allow Turkish officials to enter the consulate .","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"On Sunday , stocks on the Tadawul All-Shares Index plummeted 7 % in early trading ,","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"wiping out all the gains","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"made this year ,","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"before recovering slightly around noon .","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"In two sessions it lost $ 50bn","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"( £38bn )","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"of its $ 450bn capitalisation ,","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"AFP news agency reported .","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"Salah Shamma , of Franklin Templeton Emerging Markets Equity , told Reuters :","depth":4},{"id":90,"text":"`` The market is reacting negatively to sentiment around the Khashoggi case . ''","depth":4},{"id":91,"text":"A Turkish security source has told the BBC","depth":4},{"id":92,"text":"that officials had audio and video evidence","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"proving","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"Mr Khashoggi ,","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"who wrote for the Washington Post ,","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"was murdered inside the consulate .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Reports suggest","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"an assault and struggle took place in the consulate","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"after Mr Khashoggi entered the building","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"to get paperwork for a marriage .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"Turkish sources allege","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"he was killed by a 15-strong team of Saudi agents .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"Turkish TV has broadcast CCTV footage of the moment","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"Mr Khashoggi walked into the consulate .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":209,"left":185,"right":208,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":185,"left":115,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":110,"right":114,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":108,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":0,"r